<ptxt>
<emph>
P0222: Throttle / Pedal Position Sensor / Switch “B” Circuit Low
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of TP sensor (sub) signal circuit is lower than 0.20 V.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(1 D/C detection logic)
